About this item

  • Multi-Functional Sports Tracking & Health Monitoring: Supports over 100 sports modes including running, cycling, swimming, and more. Real-time tracking helps you reach your fitness goals. Built-in high-precision sensors monitor heart rate and blood oxygen levels, providing 24/7 health monitoring to keep your well-being at its best.
  • Special Care Features for Women: Thoughtfully designed with women's health in mind, this smartwatch can track and predict menstrual cycles, keeping you informed about your bodys changes. Combined with various health data, it provides accurate health advice, offering comfort and care to female users.
  • Smart Notifications & Bluetooth Calling: Stay connected on the go with smart notifications and Bluetooth calling. Sync your smartwatch with your phone to receive call, SMS, and app notifications directly on your wrist. The built-in Bluetooth call feature allows you to answer calls without needing to reach for your phone.
  • Variety of Watch Faces & Customization Options: With over 400 watch faces to choose from and the option to create custom designs, you can personalize your smartwatch to match your style. The sleek design and multiple color options make this smartwatch not just a functional device but also a fashion statement.
  • Long-Lasting Battery & Smart Reminders: Enjoy up to one week of battery life, reducing the need for frequent charging. The smartwatch also features smart reminders for alarms, sedentary alerts, hydration reminders, and medication alerts, helping you manage your daily routine and maintain a healthy lifestyle.

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      Amazon Customer
      5 out of 5 stars
      A Great Smart Watch!
      This is a really nice watch for a very reasonable price. Before writing this review I played around with it for five days and tried out just about every function it has. They all work. All you need to do is give it all the permissions that it requests. Theres a page in the app that you download on your phone that requests permissions. I was initially concerned that allowing it to constantly run in the background of my phone would drain my battery, and the app said that was a possibiity, but I noticed no difference in my phones battery function. In fact, it used only 6% of the battery.Setting it up the first time was a little confusing. There was one screen that had a button that should have taken me to my phones settings and it didnt work. I tapped the ignore button to get out of the screen and went to settings myself. The problem is that every phones settings are different. I have a Samsung S23. My husband has a Samsung S24. The settings are completely different. So its really impossible to provide instructions that will be accurate on every phone. One last tip is that when you get to the point where youre setting up your profile (gender, height, weight, etc) the button you need to tap to proceed to the next screen is in the center at the bottom of the screen. Its very light. If you dont know its there, you wont see it. You are also given the option to set it up for metric or imperial measurements. Once you get through the initial setup, everything works great. Like I said in the first paragraph, just give it all the permissions it wants and it will work great for you.Now the fun stuff. I guess Ill start with the appearance. It came in a very attractive box which would make for a very nice Christmas gift. The watch has 440 watch faces! I took screenshots from the app of some of them to give you an idea of whats available. With that many watch faces you have to be able to find something you like. You can also customize watch faces if you like. It comes with two different styles of watchband. Both are silicone, one has a normal watchband buckle and the other allows you to tuck the excess band between the watchband and your arm. The band size is 20mm so if you want to purchase different watchbands you can.Regarding the functionality, first I want to remind you that its connected to your phone via bluetooth so you have to keep your phone near your watch, otherwise the connection will be broken. If that happens, the watch vibrates and the dial displays a message indicating that youve lost the connection. As soon as you are back within range of your phone it automatically reconnects. I found that notification feature to be useful in preventing me from leaving my house without my phone. Ive done that a few times in the past and its very inconvenient. This watch will make sure you dont do that. The watch has so many functions that theres no way I can describe, or even list, all of them. I took a lot of pictures, though, so you can see for yourself what functions are available and what they look like on the watch face and your phone. I will discuss a few, though.You can set it up to receive all your text messages as well as notifications from social media apps like FB, Messenger, WhatsApp, Nextdoor and more. Other apps you can receive notifications from include Instagram, YouTube, Gmail, Snapchat, X and Pinterest. That list is probably not all inclusive. I tested the text message function as well as the four social media apps I just mentioned and the watch did not miss a single notification. 100% accuracy for five days! You can also answer your phone using the watch. I had my husband call me and I was able to answer the phone and speak to him through the watch while my phone was in my pocket. He said my voice came across crystal clear! I was also able to make phone calls using the watch. I didnt import my contacts because I have a lot of them. I just dialed my husband because I know his number by heart. The speaker on the watch works very well.I set seven different alarms just to test how many it would allow me to set and I can safely say you can set at least seven to go off every day. I got bored after that and didnt try to set up anymore alarms. I doubt anyone would need to set up more. The alarm goes off whether you are wearing the watch or charging it and its loud enough for you to hear. Its a really nice function.The sleep monitoring function is my favorite. It shows on the watch and your phone. Ive included photos of both. It also records your heart rate, blood oxygen record, stress record, emotion record, steps, calories burned and kilometers covered. It can be personalized to record for may different kinds of exercises including but not limited to pushups, situps, gymnastics, tennis, walking and running. It also provides weather reports as well as two different games.Like any new device youll have to play around with it to get used to it and to discover all the functionality it has to offer. You can swipe up, down, right and left to get to different menus.Im very happy with this watch. It has so much more functionality that watches that cost much more and its even waterproof. You cant go wrong with this watch. I really think youll love it.

        Ive been using it for a week now, and I am thoroughly impressed with its features, performance, and overall value. If youre looking for a reliable smartwatch with advanced health monitoring capabilities, this is definitely a great choice.
        The watch has a nice modern design that looks great on the wrist. Its lightweight and comfortable to wear all day, whether Im at work, at the gym, or out for a run. Comes with two adjustable straps that fits well, and the display is bright and easy to read, even in direct sunlight.
        One of the best things about this smartwatch is its heart rate monitoring. It provides accurate readings, which is great for keeping track of my overall health. The step counter and multi sport mode help me stay motivated throughout the day, and I love being able to see my progress in real time. So many options to choose from!
        The waterproof feature is a huge plus. Ive worn it while washing my hands and it holds up perfectly. While its not meant for swimming, its great to know that sweat and water splashes wont damage it.
        Pairing it with my IPhone was quick and easy. I get all my calls, texts and app notifications right on my wrist, which is super convenient when Im on the go. The battery life is also impressive I can go several days without needing to recharge, been a week since I got it and didnt have to charge it once.
        Overall, this is an excellent smartwatch for anyone looking to track their fitness, monitor their health, and stay connected. It offers high/end features at an affordable price, making it a fantastic value. Whether youre a fitness enthusiast or just want a stylish, functional smartwatch, I highly recommend this one! Will get another for my girlfriend!
